一：云服务器：
1.Xshell连接云服务器：Linux命令的使用
2.xftp的文件上传及下载（下载xftp）客户端
3.rz与sz的使用（rz将本地文件批量上传到远程Linux / Unix服务器，sz将多个文件从远程服务器下载到本地）
需要安装lrzsz包，安装命令：yum install lrzsz
二.Python3环境的搭建
1.Python3.6的安装
1.yum安装依赖包  避免后面出现少包的问题:
yum -y install zlib-devel bzip2-devel openssl-devel ncurses-devel sqlite-devel readline-devel tk-devel gdbm-devel db4-devel libpcap-devel xz-devel mysql-devel
2.wget下载Python版本: wget https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.6.8/Python-3.6.8.tgz
3.解压下载下来的Python压缩包: tar -xvf Python-3.6.8.tgz
4.cdPythonERF: cd Python-3.6.8
5. /configure --prefix=/root/python36
6.编译:make
7. : make install
8.iPython : In -s /root/python36/bin/python3 /usr/bin/python36
9.ipip3 : In -s /root/python36/bin/pip3 /usr/bin/pip3
设置软链接方法:In-s 要设置软链接的目录/usr/bin/软链接启动名称
三.docker环境搭建
1.docker
1.2ERE: yum install-y yum-utils device-mapper-persistent-data Ivm2
2.badockertSItt: yum-config-manager --add-repo http://mirrors.aliyun.com/docker-ce/linux/centos/docker-ce.repo
3.Frum F: yum makecache fast
4. docker: yum install docker-ce
5.把docker设置为开机启动项:sudo systemctl enable docker
Bndocker: sudo systemctl start docker
*Edocker: sudo systemctl stop docker
&Eacute;dockert: sudo systemcti status docke
四.MYSQL环境搭建
1.EAdocker : docker pull mysql:5.7
2.直看docker下所有容器:docker images
3. RER: mkdir -p -/lianzhang/mysql/config ~/lianzhang/mysql/data
4.E JMYSQL: docker run -p 3319:3306 --name lianzhang -v ~/lianzhang/mysql/conf./etc/mysql/conf.d -v -/lianzhang/mysql/logs:/logs -v -/lianzhang/mysql/data:/va
MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=123456 -d mysql:5.7
